Only the dense (`fastembed`) half of hybrid recall is optional: with the model
cache cold or fastembed unavailable, recall degrades to BM25-only. `numpy` /
`PyYAML` / `rank-bm25` are the full-fidelity path; the `_vendor/` fallbacks cover
the bare-`python3` window before bootstrap.

